name: Rubik Dirt
description: The Generative Fonts is an original, script-generated collection of fonts based on the Google Fonts Rubik by Hubert and Fischer, Meir Sadan and Cyreal. The code used to generate it can be found at github.com/NaN-xyz/Glyph-Filters . Check for more Rubik "Filtered" fonts ! To contribute, see github.com/NaN-xyz/Rubik-Filtered .
author: NaN, Luke Prowse
